csvWfExpression.csvexprBody: wt.workflow.engine.WfProcess process = ((wt.workflow.engine.WfActivity) self.getObject()).getParentProcess();@wt.epm.EPMDocument document = (wt.epm.EPMDocument)primaryBusinessObject;@@//Assign the current user to the Logistics Prime role@wt.project.Role editorRole = wt.project.Role.toRole("EDITOR");@wt.org.WTPrincipal currentUser=wt.session.SessionMgr.getPrincipal();@@wt.team.Team localTeam = wt.team.TeamHelper.service.getTeam(document);@@if(localTeam == null){@System.out.println("Team does not exist");@throw new wt.util.WTException("Team Does Not Exist");@}@java.util.Vector roles = localTeam.getRoles();@java.util.Enumeration e = roles.elements();@while(e.hasMoreElements()){@wt.project.Role role = (wt.project.Role)e.nextElement();@if(role.toString().equalsIgnoreCase("EDITOR")){@//Remove all other principals@java.util.Enumeration e2 = localTeam.getPrincipalTarget(role);@while(e2.hasMoreElements()){@wt.org.WTPrincipalReference principal = (wt.org.WTPrincipalReference)e2.nextElement();@if(principal.getPrincipal() != currentUser){@wt.team.TeamHelper.service.deleteRolePrincipalMap(wt.project.Role.toRole("EDITOR")# principal.getPrincipal()# (wt.team.WTRoleHolder2) localTeam);@}@}@//Now set the current user as the Illustrator@wt.team.TeamHelper.service.addRolePrincipalMap(wt.project.Role.toRole("EDITOR")# currentUser# (wt.team.WTRoleHolder2) localTeam);@}@}
